'''刘岩'''，中国[[南极|南极]]研究科学家，北京师范大学全球变化与地球系统科学研究院（GCESS）以及[[北京师范大学|北京师范大学]]极地研究中心地理副教授，主要研究方向为{{link-en|冰山崩解|Ice calving}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gcess.cn/yjdw/yjtd|title=北京师范大学全球变化与地球系统科学研究院|accessdate=2016-06-13|publisher=Beijing Normal University|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623083449/http://www.gcess.cn/yjdw/yjtd/|archive-date=2016-06-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 生平==
刘岩于2003在武汉大学以优秀毕业生身份获得摄影测量与遥感专业学士，于2006在中国科学院遥感应用研究所获得地图学与地理信息系统专业硕士，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://d.wanfangdata.com.cn/Thesis/J008409|title=半干旱草地NPP遥感模型和环境响应研究|accessdate=2016-06-13|date=2006}}</ref>并于2013年在北京师范大学获得全球环境变化专业博士 。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gcess.cn/yjspy/dsjj/61559.html|title=北京师范大学全球变化与地球系统科学研究院|accessdate=2016-06-13|date=2013-10-29|publisher=Beijing Normal University|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825204050/http://www.gcess.cn/yjspy/dsjj/61559.html|archive-date=2016-08-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 她于2013至2015年间在GCESS开展博士后研究，并在2014负责承担中国国家自然基金委（NSFC）项目：南极冰架物质平衡及变化。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://isisn.nsfc.gov.cn/egrantindex/funcindex/prjsearch-list|title=科学基金网络信息系统 -  项目检索|accessdate=2016-06-13|archive-date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202082536/http://isisn.nsfc.gov.cn/egrantindex/funcindex/prjsearch-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 学术成就及影响 ==
在担任三年的[[遥感|遥感]]技术应用工程师之后，刘岩于2009年开始其对南极的科学研究。她的主要研究领域包括南极冰架崩解及其对[[氣候變遷|气候变化]]的响应。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Ocean-driven thinning enhances iceberg calving and retreat of Antarctic ice shelves|url=http://www.pnas.org/content/112/11/3263|last=Liu|first=Yan|last2=Moore|first2=John C.|date=2015-03-17|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=11|doi=10.1073/pnas.1415137112|volume=112|pages=3263–3268|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmc=4371949|pmid=25733856|last3=Cheng|first3=Xiao|last4=Gladstone|first4=Rupert M.|last5=Bassis|first5=Jeremy N.|last6=Liu|first6=Hongxing|last7=Wen|first7=Jiahong|last8=Hui|first8=Fengming|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120001322/https://www.pnas.org/content/112/11/3263|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Termini of calving glaciers as self-organized critical systems|url=http://www.nature.com/ngeo/journal/v7/n12/abs/ngeo2290.html|last=Åström|first=J. A.|last2=Vallot|first2=D.|date=2014-12-01|journal=Nature Geoscience|issue=12|doi=10.1038/ngeo2290|volume=7|pages=874–878|language=en|issn=1752-0894|last3=Schäfer|first3=M.|last4=Welty|first4=E. Z.|last5=O’Neel|first5=S.|last6=Bartholomaus|first6=T. C.|last7=Liu|first7=Yan|last8=Riikilä|first8=T. I.|last9=Zwinger|first9=T.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Detection of crevasses over polar ice shelves using Satellite Laser Altimeter|url=http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11430-013-4796-x|last=Liu|first=Yan|last2=Cheng|first2=Xiao|date=2014-02-20|journal=Science China Earth Sciences|issue=6|doi=10.1007/s11430-013-4796-x|volume=57|pages=1267–1277|language=en|issn=1674-7313|last3=Hui|first3=FengMing|last4=Wang|first4=XianWei|last5=Wang|first5=Fang|last6=Cheng|first6=Cheng|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613024608/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs11430-013-4796-x|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Dynamic response of Antarctic ice shelves to bedrock uncertainty|url=http://www.the-cryosphere.net/8/1561/2014/|last=Sun|first=S.|last2=Cornford|first2=S. L.|date=2014-08-21|journal=The Cryosphere|issue=4|doi=10.5194/tc-8-1561-2014|volume=8|pages=1561–1576|issn=1994-0424|last3=Liu|first3=Y.|last4=Moore|first4=J. C.|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521093453/https://www.the-cryosphere.net/8/1561/2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她对[[冰架|冰架]]动力学的研究应用结合了包括卫星雷达和[[高度计|测高]]在内的遥感数据。她的主要学术成就在于对南极冰架物质流失特别是冰山崩解和底部融化的研究<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />，曾在中国国家南北极数据中心发表了南极冰山崩解数据库。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chinare.org.cn/en/difDetailPublic/?id=7507|title=Data-sharing Platform of Polar Science|accessdate=2016-06-13}}</ref>

刘岩是[[北京师范大学|北京师范大学]]陈晓教授极地遥感研究组的核心成员。该组的遥感数据对全南极洲地表覆盖图的绘制做出极大的贡献，<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mapping blue-ice areas in Antarctica using ETM+ and MODIS data|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/contentone/igsoc/agl/2014/00000055/00000066/art00016|last=Hui|first=Fengming|last2=Ci|first2=Tianyu|date=2014-05-01|journal=Annals of Glaciology|issue=66|doi=10.3189/2014AoG66A069|volume=55|pages=129–137|last3=Cheng|first3=Xiao|last4=Scambos|first4=Ted A.|last5=Liu|first5=Yan|last6=Zhang|first6=Yanmei|last7=Chi|first7=Zhaohui|last8=Huang|first8=Huabing|last9=Wang|first9=Xianwei}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=An improved Landsat Image Mosaic of Antarctica|url=http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11430-012-4481-5|last=Hui|first=FengMing|last2=Cheng|first2=Xiao|date=2012-08-06|journal=Science China Earth Sciences|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s11430-012-4481-5|volume=56|pages=1–12|language=en|issn=1674-7313|last3=Liu|first3=Yan|last4=Zhang|first4=YanMei|last5=Ye|first5=YuFang|last6=Wang|first6=XianWei|last7=Li|first7=Zhan|last8=Wang|first8=Kun|last9=Zhan|first9=ZhiFei|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619110857/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs11430-012-4481-5|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/tech/2012-12/01/c_124031735.htm|title=世界首张全南极洲地表覆盖图来到南极 - 新华科技 - 新华网|accessdate=2016-06-13|date=2012-12-01|publisher=Xinhua News|archive-date=2013-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515194801/http://news.xinhuanet.com/tech/2012-12/01/c_124031735.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 并为自2011年以来的南极科考中使用的破冰船[[雪龙号|“雪龙”号]]的导航提供了监控和支持，<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Sea-ice conditions in the Adélie Depression, Antarctica, during besetment of the icebreaker RV Xuelong|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/contentone/igsoc/agl/2015/00000056/00000069/art00019;jsessionid=6q0o6culsc4kg.victoria|last=Zhai|first=Mengxi|last2=Li|first2=Xinqing|date=2015-10-01|journal=Annals of Glaciology|issue=69|doi=10.3189/2015AoG69A007|volume=56|pages=160–166|last3=Hui|first3=Fengming|last4=Cheng|first4=Xiao|last5=Heil|first5=Petra|last6=Zhao|first6=Tiancheng|last7=Jiang|first7=Tianyu|last8=Cheng|first8=Cheng|last9=Ci|first9=Tianyu}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Xuelong Navigation in Fast Ice Near the Zhongshan Station, Antarctica|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/mts/mtsj/2014/00000048/00000001/art00009?crawler=true|last=Wang|first=Xianwei|last2=Cheng|first2=Xiao|date=2014-01-01|journal=Marine Technology Society Journal|issue=1|doi=10.4031/MTSJ.48.1.5|volume=48|pages=84–91|last3=Hui|first3=Fengming|last4=Cheng|first4=Cheng|last5=Fok|first5=H.S.|last6=Liu|first6=Yan}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2014/2/288339.shtm|title=程晓：为"雪龙"带路—新闻—科学网|accessdate=2016-06-13|date=2014-02-11|last=Min|first=Ren|publisher=ScienceNet|archive-date=2015-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150512224321/http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2014/2/288339.shtm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 助力“雪龙”号在2014年1月南极成功脱困 。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gdbnu.com/article.asp?id=460|title=我校科研人员助力"雪龙"号南极成功脱困|accessdate=2016-06-13|date=2014-01-09|publisher=Beijing Normal University|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160825170648/http://www.gdbnu.com/article.asp?id=460|archivedate=2016-08-25}}</ref>

刘岩使用卫星图像对全南极海岸线1平方公里以上的冰山的崩解以及冰架的健康状况做出了测量。她的研究发现，虽然其中许多小型冰架在萎缩但一些大型冰架还在增长。经历着由底部融化引起的变薄的南极冰架拥有高冰山崩解速率，表明南极冰架对海洋的强迫作用的敏感度超出以前研究的估计。<ref name=":0"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/technology/science-research/article/1754095/antarctica-losing-enough-ice-every-year-fill|title=Antarctica losing enough ice every year to fill the Three Gorges reservoir 19 times|accessdate=2016-06-13|date=2015-04-06|publisher=South China Morning Post|archive-date=2016-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119123514/http://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/technology/science-research/article/1754095/antarctica-losing-enough-ice-every-year-fill|dead-url=no}}</ref>

